## Sensitivity Classification

All data used in this pipeline is classified according to the [UK Government Security Classifications](https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/government-security-classifications):

- **Official**: The majority of government data. Standard security controls apply.
- **Official-Sensitive**: Requires additional handling controls. Must not be committed to Git.

> **Note**: Never commit raw data files containing personal or sensitive information to version control. Use `.gitignore` to exclude data files and document access instructions here instead.

